Package io.github.eutro.jwasm

Class ExprVisitor

java.lang.Object
io.github.eutro.jwasm.BaseVisitor<ExprVisitor>
io.github.eutro.jwasm.ExprVisitor
Direct Known Subclasses:
ConstantExprValidator, ExprNode, ExprValidator, ExprWriter
public class ExprVisitor
extends BaseVisitor<ExprVisitor>
A visitor that visits an expression.

Methods are expected to be called in the order:

( visitInsn | visitPrefixInsn | visitConstInsn | visitNullInsn | visitFuncInsn | visitSelectInsn | visitVariableInsn | visitTableInsn | visitPrefixTableInsn | visitPrefixBinaryTableInsn | visitMemInsn | visitIndexedMemInsn | visitBlockInsn | visitElseInsn | visitEndInsn | visitBreakInsn | visitTableBreakInsn | visitCallInsn | visitCallIndirectInsn )* visitEnd

    • visitPrefixInsn

      public void visitPrefixInsn​(int opcode)
      Visit a prefix instr, one encoded with Opcodes.INSN_PREFIX followed by a variable-length u32 representing the actual opcode.

      It has no immediate arguments.

      Parameters:
      opcode - The integer opcode of the instruction.
